WEBVTT

00:02.726 --> 00:05.646
I have been... angry...

00:08.246 --> 00:10.086
jealous.

00:11.086 --> 00:13.126
I have given in to self-pity.

00:16.806 --> 00:19.446
Do you have any mortal sins
to confess?

00:20.446 --> 00:22.166
I have...

00:23.166 --> 00:27.126
loved... outside of marriage.

00:28.446 --> 00:32.406
Violet, many people return
to the fold when they face death.

00:34.446 --> 00:36.285
But they cannot find true salvation

00:36.286 --> 00:38.646
if they hide
their selves from God.

00:40.126 --> 00:44.046
If you killed your husband,
don't you want to confess?

00:45.486 --> 00:49.886
Tell his family where the body
is and clear your conscience?

00:55.166 --> 00:57.205
Violet...

00:57.206 --> 00:59.366
From the Lord Chief Justice?

01:05.446 --> 01:07.486
They turned it down?

01:08.806 --> 01:12.006
Appeal unsuccessful.

01:20.326 --> 01:22.846
You know now that death is certain.

01:24.566 --> 01:26.486
Confess...

01:27.486 --> 01:30.046
so that God can forgive your sin.

01:31.766 --> 01:34.965
I can't admit
what I didn't do, Father.

01:34.966 --> 01:38.245
I'm not guilty, I am innocent.

01:38.246 --> 01:40.445
Help me, please!

01:40.446 --> 01:43.686
We have to take you in now.
You can't do this!

